dgment.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 0aDeconstruction. 0aDeconstructivism (Architecture). 4aLiterature : Literary Theory. 4aPhilosophy : Continental Philosophy. 4aPhilosophy : Philosophy. 7aPHILOSOPHY / Movements / Deconstruction.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978143846002440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781438460024423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781438460024/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles